Method Detail

computeFirst

public TermSet computeFirst(java.util.Vector<Symbol> alpha)
This method will be use in fillFirstSet and fillFollowSet methods, to be able to compute the first set and return the term set it check if the length of string of symbol alpha, if the length is zero, then it will return the set of lambda. if the length of alpha is greater than zero, then the result will be the union of the current result subtract the set of lambda. until it iterates to the size of alpha, it will union the result with the set of lambda

alpha -
Returns:
